OL,3,CWhy we should be concerned that Mr
OL,4,CBates vs The Post Office made a #1m
OL,5,Closs
OL,7,GIt's been the TV drama of the year so
OL,8,Gfar. Mr Bates vs The Post Office was
OL,9,Gevent TV, won good overnight viewing
OL,10,Gfigures and brought the Horizon
OL,11,Gscandal back to public attention.
OL,13,FIt was also relatively cheap for a
OL,14,Fdrama. It was not a lavish production
OL,15,Fand some of the cast apparently
OL,16,Faccepted lower fees than they might
OL,17,Fhave been able to command.
OL,19,FYet ITV says it has lost more than #1m
OL,20,Fon the series.
