OL,3,CWhy we should be concerned that Mr
OL,4,CBates vs The Post Office made a #1m
OL,5,Closs
OL,7,FThis is profoundly depressing and
OL,8,Fworrying.
OL,10,FThe economics of commercial
OL,11,Fbroadcasting are complex. It's about
OL,12,Fmore than what a programme attracts in
OL,13,Fad revenue.
OL,15,FFor a start some programmes will be
OL,16,Ffunded entirely by one broadcaster `
OL,17,Fothers will be co-productions with two
OL,18,For more partners.
OL,20,FProduct placement may also augment the
OL,21,Fbudget.
