OL,3,CWhy we should be concerned that Mr
OL,4,CBates vs The Post Office made a #1m
OL,5,Closs
OL,7,FAgainst this comes the return on the
OL,8,Finvestment ` advertising during the
OL,9,Fscreening, sponsorship, sales to other
OL,10,Fchannels, DVD sales, international
OL,11,Fsales.
OL,13,FITV hasn't given a full public
OL,14,Fexplanation of the losses but
OL,15,Fpresumably there are two key factors.
OL,17,FFirstly the amount of advertising
OL,18,Fduring the programme. What was the
OL,19,Fairtime worth despite the good ratings?
