OL,3,CWhy we should be concerned that Mr
OL,4,CBates vs The Post Office made a #1m
OL,5,Closs
OL,7,FToday you would assume all output
OL,8,Fwhich is not a legal obligation is
OL,9,Fdesigned to be profitable.
OL,11,FThe worrying thing is that pressure
OL,12,Ffrom investors could lead to even more
OL,13,Foutput which is cheap (or at least
OL,14,Fcost effective) or which will sell
OL,15,Fwell to digital channels and overseas
OL,16,Fbroadcasters.
