OL,3,CWhy we should be concerned that Mr
OL,4,CBates vs The Post Office made a #1m
OL,5,Closs
OL,7,FIt is difficult to see what can be
OL,8,Fdone to stop this. A commercial
OL,9,Fbroadcaster cannot in any sense be
OL,10,Fobliged to run "loss-making" drama.
OL,11,FPresumably if a programme was not a
OL,12,FPSB obligation it was never meant to
OL,13,Flose money in the first place.
OL,15,FBut would finally abandoning the
OL,16,Flimits on advertising on C3, C4 and C5
OL,17,Fpotentially help make losses easier to
OL,18,Fstomach?
