OL,3,CWhy we should be concerned that Mr
OL,4,CBates vs The Post Office made a #1m
OL,5,Closs
OL,7,FWith this pressure on commercial
OL,8,Fbroadcasters, it is more important
OL,9,Fthan ever for the BBC to continue to
OL,10,Finvest in a full range of drama ` some
OL,11,Fof which will get low ratings and not
OL,12,Fsell well outside the UK.
OL,14,FC4 should have a role too: in its
OL,15,Fbattle against privatisation it
OL,16,Femphasised how popular, profitable
OL,17,Foutput allowed it to subsidise non-
OL,18,Fcommercial activity.
OL,20,FIn recent years this has been far less
OL,21,Fobvious to viewers than was once the
OL,22,Fcase.
