OL,3,CWhy we should be concerned that Mr
OL,4,CBates vs The Post Office made a #1m
OL,5,Closs
OL,7,FMore bold commissions would certainly
OL,8,Fmake it easier to argue C4 should stay
OL,9,Fin the public sector long term.
OL,11,FBut frankly, news Mr Bates vs The Post
OL,12,FOffice lost money should be setting
OL,13,Foff alarm bells.
OL,15,FIt is the sort of TV which all major
OL,16,Fbroadcasters ` including mainstream
OL,17,Fcommercial channels ` should aspire to
OL,18,Fproducing.
